name: mega_compare_variadic_gt_with_do_operands
section: codegen-compare-variadic
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int setup:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Variadic > must evaluate do/begin operands and then compare adjacent values.
law: (= (> (do {setup} {a}) (begin {setup} {b}) {c}) (> {a} {b} {c}))
